{"tid":2034200,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(五毛認證）港獨已成中共自我實現預言","createTime":"2020-05-25T05:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T14:32:03.000Z","uid":324193,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2bfcebe0ebe0f5e87a21b1482d81979ea25bdbdd","tid":2034200,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T05:58:14.000Z","msg":"//筆者要問一個問題：「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">假如一國兩制不是一個前途選項，在一國一制與港獨之間，市民會如何選擇？</span></span>」在國安法立法如箭在弦之時，市民對一國兩制「結束」感到害怕，不論是網民對 VPN 的討論、對移民的搜尋數字上升，還是股市大跌，都意味到港人對一國一制的恐懼。如果中共以為繼續宣傳國安法可令一國兩制屹立不倒，港人就會相信未來「一國兩制」依然行之有效，未免太看小港人的智慧，港人會思考未來政制的出路，而「一國兩制」被強姦之後，難道還會有人問強姦犯拿回自己的貞操嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港獨並非以一個合法政權的形式存在，而是以流亡政府的方式在世界各地進行「復國運動」</span></span>。港人擁有的海外連結和資金比西藏流亡政府更多，當國際戰線演變為「流亡政府線」，香港問題必會在以後幾十年變成國際外交問題，如果幸運的話，港人會像以色列人一樣復國成功，不幸的話便成了無家可歸、建國無期的巴勒斯坦人，但是港人無可避免要在重光前經歷一段相當長的黑暗日子。<br />\n<br />\n不論你是什麼角色，中共總能為你找到勾結港獨份子的罪證，而讀者不是以為做一個港豬順民，便可避過文革 2.0 的批鬥港獨份子大會，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在一國一制下的香港，本身香港人的身份便是原罪，並淪為危害國家安全的二等公民</span></span>。中共親自為每一個香港人扣上港獨帽子，在「去港獨化」的過程中必會造成不同的冤獄、甚至殺戮，700 萬港獨份子，你準備好了嗎？//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E5%B7%B2%E6%88%90%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E5%AF%A6%E7%8F%BE%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E7%258F%25BE%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25A8%2580%2F&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3swxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=902b5812\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E7%258F%25BE%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25A8%2580%2F&h=33e29b53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E5%B7%B2%E6%88%90%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E5%AF%A6%E7%8F%BE%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%80/</a>"},{"pid":"b26acf32642e9a0937134740517cb6e766163f05","tid":2034200,"uid":324193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T06:00:57.000Z","msg":"補返五毛認證先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GdqVruW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGdqVruW.png&h=fa92a223&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c813fb5a90dc63bbaa4f24d044855954c9220016","tid":2034200,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T06:04:02.000Z","msg":"黎明前既黑暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233e74e84069e56e86cd56f581016d21a2928ae4","tid":2034200,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T06:13:18.000Z","msg":"不如諗下點搞流亡政府/議會線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c61c2417b207341b13a50b4b165239efa41a94","tid":2034200,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T06:27:29.000Z","msg":"中共自作自受，有暴政先有港獨"},{"pid":"5d68410e4613020cbf47e43fb6dfc66ec0d3c8bf","tid":2034200,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:27:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d6f806548d09684946cc5ea104098084bc10b5","tid":2034200,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:32:03.000Z","msg":"有懶人包<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112157957141912/posts/130262731998101/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112157957141912%2Fposts%2F130262731998101%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3swxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=7